            <title>[CASSANDRA-14091] DynamicSnitch creates a lot of garbage</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14091</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
